Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Contemporary two level commercial office set around a central atrium area that provides abundant natural light throughout and outstanding staff amenity.

Part or whole building offering via sub lease until June 2023, or longer via direct lease.

Located on the border of Subiaco, this building is in proximity to an abundance of retail and public transport amenity.

The building has been refurbished throughout to provide high quality office accommodation with a combination of meeting rooms, offices, open plan workstations and kitchen/breakout areas.

Flexible offerings from 1000 - 1400sqm

High parking ratio available.

For any queries, please contact the exclusive leasing agents.

54 Salvado Road, Wembley - 

Prominent two level office building with secure basement car parking, occupying a high exposure location on the corner of Salvado Road and Harborne Street.

Building signage rights available!

The building is located on the border of Wembley and Subiaco, within walking distance to Subiaco Train Station, St John of God Hospital and excellent retail amenity. 

NABERS Rating - 4.0 Stars.

Partitioned or open plan office accommodation available 

The side-core configuration of the building provides for functional floor plates, excellent natural light and self-contained amenities.

This tenancy is currently partitioned with a high number of offices and meeting facilities, however the owner can alter the fitout.

Level 1 - 681 sqm

Partitioned or open plan tenancy which currently incorporates a high number of perimeter offices, internal meeting rooms, kitchen and bathroom facilities.

EOT facilities including showers and bicycle parking.

Outgoings - Payable by the Lessee and currently estimated at $155.82/sqm.

High parking ratio of 1 bay per 47sqm
